This code has been developed by Matt Bunting, extending work done by Jonathan Sprinkle and originally based on code by:
NetGroup, Politecnico di Torino (Italy)
CACE Technologies, Davis (California)
See readVelodyne.cpp for details about the original distribution.

Alex Warren modified this code to provide point cloud files to the
WITTI app. Details on its usage can be found in the src/README.txt


Dependencies
* PCAP library
  in ubuntu:
  > sudo apt-get install libpcap-dev
* cmake

Installation

> mkdir build && cd build
> cmake ..
> make -j